{{Otheruses|Ancients}}
The '''Ancients''' were worshiped as deities by the age-revering [[Klatooinian/Legends|Klatooinian]] people. From the earliest period in their recorded history, the Klatooinians believed in the idea of strength through age, as exemplified by the [[Fountain of Ancients]]. This spectacular formation was considered a gift of the Ancients, inspiring them to tenacity, patience, and respect for tradition.<ref name="Galaxy Guide 12">''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]''</ref>

After the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]] made contact with the Klatooinians and signed them into servitude, the long-lived gastropods were identified with the Ancients. Millennia later, however, younger Klatooinians who wanted freedom from their Hutt overlords disputed this.<ref name="Galaxy Guide 12" />

